2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">活结乐队</a>在加利福尼亚州发布了一个神秘的广告牌，上面写着“仅限一晚”，以此来预告一场即将举行的神秘活动。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="94" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353"><b>Slipknot 的 Clown 谈论 2024 年巡演和新材料：“这支乐队从未如此快乐”</b></a></li></ul><p>上周，这则明显的广告出现在通往<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">2024 年科切拉音乐节</a>的高速公路上的广告牌上，上面有乐队的标志以及第二个口号“LONG MAY YOU DIE”。</p><p>横幅上还包含<a href="https://youcantkillme.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">youcantkillme.com</a>的链接，这是一个复古网站，其中引用了乐队 1999 年的同名专辑（来自<a href="https://www.revolvermag.com/music/slipknot-tease-one-night-only-event-mysterious-desert-billboard" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Revolver</i></a> ）。</p><p>该网站还载有乐队即将举行的演唱会日期，并附有一条说明，该页面的最新更新时间为 4 月 25 日（即下周）。总而言之，歌迷们开始猜测乐队可能正在为《Slipknot》专辑举办 25 周年纪念演出。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="活结 - 等待和流血 [官方视频] [高清]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/B1zCN0YhW1s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>与此同时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-a-new-slipknot-song-be-coming-soon-3600684">，关于乐队新音乐的谣言已经在他们的粉丝群中蔓延</a>。</p><p>新金属偶像们发行的最后一张专辑是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/slipknot-the-end-so-far-review-3317936">《The End, So Far》</a> ，于 2022 年 8 月发行。事实证明，这是两位键盘手 Craig Jones 离开之前的最后一张完整专辑，后者于 6 月离开了乐队，还有不久后突然被踢出阵容的杰伊·温伯格（Jay Weinberg）。</p><p>从那以后，活结乐队一直<a href="https://www.nme.com/photos/music-photos/slipknot-tease-mystery-new-drummer-in-rehearsal-photo-3599624">在向粉丝们暗示新鼓手的消息，并在网上发布了一张破损的鼓槌的照片，并配上“排练”的标题。</a>然而，根据帖子的评论，乐队的现场演出似乎超出了计划。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4UOMmPxA8r/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 52